about.summary: Swig generated Python bindings to the Community Sensor Model API

name: csmapi
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "csmapi" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/USGS-Astrogeology/swigcsm/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 81a6914facb91cf4d5e7156b59eb37d75c598b13d8de467852e43dac69a6bc58

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake >=3.10
    - swig
    - python >=3.5
  host:
    - csm
    - python >=3.5
    - setuptools
  run:
    - csm
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - csmapi

about:
  home: http://github.com/USGS-Astrogeology/swigcsm
  license: Public Domain
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Swig generated Python bindings to the Community Sensor Model API

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jlaura
    - kelvinrr
